Package: fastrenameR
Title: Fast FASTA Header Renaming Using Metadata with Date Standardization
Version: 0.2.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Serigne Fallou Mbacke", "NGOM", 
           email = "serignefalloumb.ngom@gmail.com",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0009-0000-8818-047X"))
Description: Fast and flexible renaming of Pathoplexus FASTA sequence 
    headers using metadata files. Supports gzipped files, automatic 
    sanitisation, and includes date standardization for BEAST/BEAUti 
    compatibility. Convert various date formats (Month-Day-Year, 
    Month-Year, Decimal year, Year only) to ISO standard (YYYY-MM-DD).
